            "rearRight": "blue"
        },
        "derpy": true,
        "bio": "Sullivan James Sherwood IV is a duck of refined skill and quiet confidence. Known around the pond as both a gamer and a streamer, Sullivan has a knack for mastering any challenge that comes its way. Whether navigating complicated mazes of lily pads or coordinating with other ducks during intense pond-side competitions, Sullivan approaches every situation like a well-planned strategy game.\nWhen the action heats up, Sullivan naturally slips into streamer mode \u2014 narrating the moment, keeping the energy high, and somehow making even the most chaotic adventures look smooth and entertaining. Other ducks gather nearby just to watch and learn, because Sullivan has a way of turning everyday pond life into a highlight reel.\nBut what really sets Sullivan apart is being genuinely smart. Behind the cool gamer persona is a sharp mind that quickly figures out puzzles, solves problems, and helps teammates level up their own skills. If there\u2019s a tricky bug to fix, a path to optimize, or a clever plan to form, Sullivan James Sherwood IV is already three moves ahead.",
        "date": {
            "$date": "2026-03-04T00:00:00Z"
        },
        "approved": true,
        "stats": {
            "strength": 5,
            "health": 5,
            "focus": 5,
            "intelligence": 10,
            "kindness": 5
        },
        "__v": 0,
